programme.title: Nick of Time

programme.title: Fantastic Four

programme.title: Jurassic Park III
programme.desc: When a mysterious couple convinces Dr. Grant to take them to Isla Sorna, he later discovers that they have a hidden motive after they become stuck on the island with its deadly inhabitants.(n)

programme.title: Ride Along

When they get into a heated argument at a Chinese restaurant, a woman comes in and gives them a fortune cookie that will get them to switch their lives. How will each of them see the other one's life.(n)

programme.title: Up
programme.desc: By tying thousands of balloons to the roof of his house, elderly Carl intends to make his dream of seeing South America's prairies come true. When he takes off, he realizes that he is not alone on his trip, for little Russel unintentionally came along for the ride.(n)

programme.title: Cinderella II: Dreams Come True
programme.desc: After the Prince found Cinderella and married her ,they lived a wonderful romantic story in the palace. In her early days, Cinderella suffers from unusual royal customs and learns to become a princess. But at the same time without giving up the company of her old friends, she also helps one of her annoying stepsisters to find true love.(n)

programme.title: Frozen
programme.desc: Princess Elsa (Idina Menzel) has power to create ice, but she suppressed it because of an accident that nearly killed her sister Anna (Kristen Bell). During Elsa's inauguration as a queen, things get out of hand and Elsa escapes. Anna decides to accompany Kristoff and Olaf on a journey to find Elsa and save the kingdom.(n)

programme.title: Beauty and the Beast
programme.desc: An adaptation of the Disney animated fairy tale in which Belle is a bright and independent young girl who is taken captive by a beast in his castle in exchange for releasing her father who accidentally trespassed into that castle. Despite her fear, she learns to befriend the castle's enchanted staff and is able to see beyond the beast's exterior to realise the true heart of the prince within. Belle and the beast fall in love when Gaston, an arrogant hunter, sets out to hunt the beast and take Belle to himself at any cost.(n)
